{"tid":758933,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【舊歌分享】有冇人金鍾意聽陳百強(Danny仔)既歌？","createTime":"2018-07-28T06:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T03:04:29.000Z","uid":11485,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"55a3211bdb08b2f93b0be59cbb7a7a0954b28591","tid":758933,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"未聽過陳百強既可以先聽下佢經典代表作先：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">眼淚為你流\n喝采\n幾分鐘的約會\n有了你\n念親恩\n漣漪\n今宵多珍重\n偏偏喜歡你\n相思河畔\n等\n摘星\n盼望的緣份\n深愛著你\n不再問究竟\n戀愛預告\n當我想起你\n一生何求</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n陳百強出名既歌都主要係前中期，但其實Danny仔中後期既歌都好好聽，不過呢個年代唔係咁多人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享下一啲我覺得陳百強好聽既冷門歌：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我和你\n明日又如何\n夢境\n迷失中有著你\n夢囈\n漫長盼望\n從今以後\n冬戀\n冷暖風鈴\n對不對\n從新欣賞我\n半生人\n寂寞的感覺\n心痛\n而情是近\n歌者戀歌\n只因愛你\n親愛的您\n離不開</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n希望可以吸引多啲人聽陳百強既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767fff4f5b5dcb177bd693cedc3b2e207953cd70","tid":758933,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a7470a49f10d1ede21814e8707ad35b14ba5ca","tid":758933,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697559faa3b314fdb9a0b6df5696644fa9916339","tid":758933,"uid":11485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adea65c1f10a2ee9acadf82ebc3b6c6260272c34","tid":758933,"uid":130849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"有呀 同好! 真係好com聽呀佢D歌 最近聽緊 冷風中, 兩心痴, 愛在今宵, 是你, 誰是知己, 過去...永遠都如此, 情人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as